sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant MW as Rate Limit<br/>Middleware
    participant Cfg as Config Service<br/>(rules + pub/sub)
    participant Store as Counter Store<br/>(sharded, atomic)
    participant BE as Backend

    C->>GW: request
    GW->>MW: forward + identity, endpoint
    MW->>Cfg: lookup rule (local cache)
    Cfg-->>MW: algo, limit, window
    MW->>Store: atomic check+incr (Lua)
    alt within limit
        Store-->>MW: count, allowed
        MW->>BE: forward request
        BE-->>C: 200 OK + X-RateLimit-* headers
    else over limit
        Store-->>MW: count, denied
        MW-->>C: 429 + Retry-After
    else store unreachable
        Store--xMW: timeout
        Note over MW: circuit-break, fail open
        MW->>BE: forward request
        BE-->>C: 200 OK
    end
